Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:03.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}生き抜くたび　隣にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}構え
